{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "patient_engagement_team", "channel": "patient_growth", "user": "michael_johnson", "message": "That's great news, Ryan! Those 250 new registrations really indicate that we are reaching our target audience effectively. It might be worth exploring how we can enhance our engagement tactics on these platforms to convert more leads into active patients.", "create_at": 1620500005000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "social_media_insights", "user": "jessica_lee", "message": "Absolutely! Since we know that social media is a strong channel for patient acquisition, we should analyze the demographics of these new patients. Understanding who they are can help us tailor our content even better to meet their needs.", "create_at": 1620500010000}}
